{"tid":1728700,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"LIHKG Misic Awards 2019 (連登討論區最愛男歌手五強投票post)","createTime":"2019-11-17T03:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T15:42:57.000Z","uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99d8e753849819b1c0b7b361cda52d538a23b20d","tid":1728700,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>***原定投票於11月15日進行，但由於當時中文大學及社會事件影響，實在難以成為音樂投票出post的合適時機，僅此抱歉。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>連登討論區最愛男歌手</strong></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">五強投票</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyKCfXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyKCfXU.jpg&h=4a45996e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男歌手五強片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UiUBl4L4hug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUiUBl4L4hug&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=d637c429\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UiUBl4L4hug</a><br />\n<br />\n五強男女歌手投票開始，於男女歌手獨立投票post，尋找所屬歌手歌名留言，並按下正皮，最終會計算「正負皮淨值」分數，並選出金銀銅獎<br />\n<br />\n以下將會有五強的名字出現，每個留言一個，按照自己所屬喜好按下正皮或負皮投票，結果將會計算由正皮減去負皮的淨直，投票截止時間為11月20日，晚上11時59分，並隨即點算結果選出金、銀、銅、獎<br />\n<br />\n感謝各位參與，亦請大家再移玉步到女歌手投票post進行投票，並於連登十大金曲post在20強內選出十強名單，同時誕生三甲獎項。"},{"pid":"d6496b42d9c2e6627c2cd9d0b997dc679707287b","tid":1728700,"uid":125502,"like":7,"dislike":11,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:44:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">張敬軒</span>"},{"pid":"bb9a416eb8ba19b634aa5a4c953e2ef50e143982","tid":1728700,"uid":125502,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">陳健安</span>"},{"pid":"49da083d4d07f0e4c0b9ccc6e4f5a6228712cefc","tid":1728700,"uid":125502,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:44:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">許廷鏗</span>"},{"pid":"7878776fa7947a107bb777225b78d63d760884a6","tid":1728700,"uid":125502,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">林家謙</span>"},{"pid":"73c2a41a62721c436b3c1fc7fe4f8d2ab7b2a0bf","tid":1728700,"uid":125502,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:45:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">韓子亮</span>"},{"pid":"96d340f473030f32699ad9a89215f7545141f259","tid":1728700,"uid":323219,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:49:48.000Z","msg":"張敬軒"},{"pid":"bbb08c4bf1f0af2bdb39028db8d2a306649e742c","tid":1728700,"uid":48318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:51:20.000Z","msg":"投hk protest yes, 投no bts<br />\n<a href=\"https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-2019/?go=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2Fperson-of-the-year-poll-2019%2F%3Fgo%3Dtrue&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=892104ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-2019/?go=true</a>"},{"pid":"3316e66978f72011402caa75adf862bc78ab4167","tid":1728700,"uid":311410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"P 牌評唔到分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林家謙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}